{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up as an army soldier in the middle of a mutant apocalypse, trying to figure out what the hell happened and blasting some heads on the way. <strong>Deadshot</strong> is a retro styled first person shooter inspired from classics like <strong>Half Life</strong>, <strong>Doom</strong>, <strong>Quake</strong> and many alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Something happened to the world overnight, everyone either became a mutant or is dead and it seems like you're the only one who can figure out what happened and put a stop to it. Go through tunnels, laboratories, buildings and storage areas, exploring for secrets, finding items to progress and killing mutants to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a <strong>3 chapter campaign</strong> with <strong>6 levels each</strong>, <strong>7 different weapons</strong>, <strong>5 weapon attachments</strong>, <strong>tons of killing</strong> all while listening to <strong>badass music</strong> composed by White Eyes, Noxtromo and Torturerr.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Freedom?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484180/cda5768dc234e4f69ffdffa0b6d738bae72003ef.jpg"},{"name":"Ubexer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484180/671bac1506acdf058da264a44fbea79644d8731e.jpg"},{"name":"Dead end","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484180/62db367b9b4662f7c06672c3ef065badba96f67a.jpg"},{"name":"Secrets?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484180/545837c57c0d8c9bfa58d9d6d5ae35ce75cd1c9a.jpg"},{"name":"Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2484180/94dba7bb4b243e59bea26304fa577ee9c60771ac.jpg"},{"name":"Gotta go fast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/ap